    <text>
        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_kūsyn" xml:lang="os">
                <form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>kūsyn</orth><form type="participle"
                            ><orth>k˳yst</orth></form></form>
                <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>kosun</orth><form
                        type="participle"><orth>kust</orth></form></form>
                <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>работать</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>work</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>трудиться</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>labour</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                <re>
                    <re>
                        <form type="lemma"><orth>kūsæg</orth></form>
                        <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>рабочий</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>worker</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re>
                        <form type="lemma"><orth>k˳yst</orth></form>
                        <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>работа</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>work (n.)</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re>
                        <form type="lemma"><orth>magūsa</orth></form>
                        <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>бездельник</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>idler</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                </re>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>kūsy ta</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>снова работает</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>he is working again</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"
                            /><biblScope>103</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>k˳yst — cardæn færæz</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>работа — опора жизни</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>work is the support of life</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>55</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Сближается с <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>kūsīdan</w>
                        <gloss><q>стараться</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>напрягать силы</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
                        <w>kūš-</w>
                        <gloss><q>to search for</q></gloss></mentioned> (? <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Konow._SSt."/><biblScope>153</biblScope></bibl>). Надежных
                    древнеиранских соответствий не видно.%n<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>III 145</biblScope></bibl>;
                            <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._Gr."/><biblScope>20, 27,
                            61</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Hübschmann._Oss."/><biblScope>45</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">It is closely related to <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>kūsīdan</w>
                        <gloss><q>endeavour</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>exert</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
                        <w>kūš-</w>
                        <gloss><q>to search for</q></gloss></mentioned> (? <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Konow._SSt."/><biblScope>153</biblScope></bibl>). There are
                    no reliable Old Iranian correspondent words. %n<bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._ОЭ"/><biblScope>III 145</biblScope></bibl>;
                            <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Вс._Миллер._Gr."/><biblScope>20, 27,
                            61</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl"
                            target="#ref_Hübschmann._Oss."/><biblScope>45</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
            </entry>
